description:
MUSASHI Intra-Workout is a scientifically formulated high performance blend that contains a matrix of Branched Chain Amino acids (BCAAs), Essential amino acids (EAAs), with Glutamine and Ornithine, as well as vitamins and minerals including magnesium to support muscle protein synthesis*. . Designed for intra-workout consumption, this advanced formulation is designed specifically to meet the needs of athletes whether competing on the field or working out on the gym floor.
Easy mix ability, a delicious taste and high strength ingredients act as an intra-workout catalyst to take your game or gym session to the next level.

BCAA, EAA & MINERAL COMPLEX
SUPPORTS ENERGY & PERFORMANCE
MAGNESIUM & B6 TO REDUCE FATIGUE
name: Musashi 350G
